item.title: Steroid Tablets consequences - tips & howtos
item.description: Steroid Tablets consequences Look into your LDL cholesterol, cortisol, endogenous hormones, liver, blood sugar, estrogens. For the elongated cycle take HCG gonadotropin to maintain the balls at volume. With the gear that aromatize get Anastrozol. Review biochemistry and testosterone levels, relax around eight weeks right after AAS phase. In between rounds provide some rest, in case the clinical tests turn like in the start - you could cycle next one.
